 {\rm g}\left(t\right) = {1 \over 2\pi}\,{1 \over 1 - {\rm i}t}\quad \mbox{is}\quad {\rm G}\left(w\right) = {\rm e}^{-\omega}\quad \mbox{for}\quad \omega > 0\ \mbox{and}\ 0\ \mbox{otherwise.} 
