 \frac{1}{2\pi}\int_{-\infty}^\infty \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} wt}G(w)\, dw= \frac{1}{2\pi}\int_{0}^\infty \mathrm{e}^{\mathrm{i} wt}\mathrm{e}^{-w} dw. 
